	(descr "iseg APS series programmable DC-HV converter module, 7-pin THT, body 39.6 x 15.7 x 11 mm. Body outline is ASYMMETRIC about the pin array (+0.60 mm long axis, +0.23 mm short axis) per Figure 1. Pad 6 = HV output, carries a 5.00 mm local clearance override. Hand solder only (270 C / 10 s / 1.5 mm from case). iseg APS series technical documentation v2.5, 2024-08-20")
